<Bill bill-origin="commons" bill-type="private-public" xml:lang="en" date-time="2010-03-11 15:09:37"><Identification><BillNumber>C-210</BillNumber><Parliament><Session>1</Session><Number>42</Number><RegnalYear><Year-s>64-65-66-67</Year-s><Monarch>Elizabeth II</Monarch></RegnalYear><Year-s>2015-2016-2017-2018</Year-s></Parliament><LongTitle>An Act to amend the National Anthem Act (gender)</LongTitle><ShortTitle status="unofficial" /><RunningHead>An Act to amend the National Anthem Act (gender)</RunningHead><BillHistory><Stages stage="assented-to"><Date><YYYY>2018</YYYY><MM>2</MM><DD>7</DD></Date></Stages></BillHistory><Chapter><ConsolidatedNumber /><AnnualStatuteId><AnnualStatuteNumber>1</AnnualStatuteNumber><YYYY>2018</YYYY></AnnualStatuteId></Chapter><BillRefNumber date-time="2010-03-11">421091</BillRefNumber></Identification><Introduction><Summary><TitleText>SUMMARY</TitleText><Provision><Text>This enactment amends the <XRefExternal reference-type="act">National Anthem Act</XRefExternal> to substitute the words ГўВЂВњof usГўВЂВќ for the words ГўВЂВњthy sonsГўВЂВќ in the English version of the national anthem, thus making it gender neutral.</Text></Provision></Summary><Enacts><Provision><MarginalNote><HistoricalNote>R.S., c. N-2</HistoricalNote></MarginalNote><Text>Her Majesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Senate and House of Commons of Canada, <Keep>enacts</Keep> as follows:</Text></Provision></Enacts></Introduction><Body><Section type="amending"><Label>1</Label><Text>The schedule to the <XRefExternal reference-type="act">National Anthem Act</XRefExternal> is replaced by the schedule set out in the schedule to this Act.</Text></Section></Body><Schedule spanlanguages="no" bilingual="yes"><RunningHead>National Anthem (gender)</RunningHead><ScheduleFormHeading type="amending"><Label>SCHEDULE / ANNEXE</Label><OriginatingRef>(Section 1 / article 1)</OriginatingRef></ScheduleFormHeading><Schedule><ScheduleFormHeading><Label>SCHEDULE / ANNEXE</Label><OriginatingRef>(Section 2 / article 2)</OriginatingRef><TitleText>National Anthem ГўВЂВ” Hymne national</TitleText><TitleText>O Canada</TitleText></ScheduleFormHeading><Provision><Text>ГўВЂВѓ</Text></Provision><ImageGroup width="34" position="center" bilingual="yes"><Image source="Hymne national - Part 1.jpg" /></ImageGroup><Provision><Text>ГўВЂВѓ</Text></Provision><ImageGroup position="center" width="34" bilingual="yes"><Image source="Hymne national - part 2.jpg" /></ImageGroup><Provision><Text>ГўВЂВѓ</Text></Provision></Schedule></Schedule></Bill>